{"type":"message","id":"5f08cc4b","parentId":"70024803","timestamp":"2026-03-09T21:02:27.200Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-03-09 16:02 CDT] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: Message for Kelly: Tony says he loves the team. Start now on QA review: define a compact QA checklist for mission control outputs (correctness, freshness, dedupe, actionability)."}],"timestamp":1773090147197}}
{"type":"message","id":"15661495","parentId":"5f08cc4b","timestamp":"2026-03-09T21:02:30.997Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Message for Kelly: Tony says he loves the team.\n\nStarted on the QA review: Defined a compact QA checklist for mission control outputs covering correctness, freshness, deduplication, and actionability.\n\nHere is the compact QA checklist:\n\n1. Correctness\n   - Verify factual accuracy of all information.\n   - Confirm proper data sources and references.\n   - Check calculations and logical consistency.\n\n2. Freshness\n   - Ensure data and information are up-to-date.\n   - Confirm timestamps and update intervals are accurate.\n   - Validate recent changes and updates are reflected.\n\n3. Deduplication\n   - Identify and remove duplicate entries or outputs.\n   - Check for redundant alerts or messages.\n   - Consolidate overlapping or repetitive information.\n\n4. Actionability\n   - Confirm clear, actionable recommendations or next steps.\n   - Ensure instructions are unambiguous and understandable.\n   - Verify priority and urgency are clearly indicated.\n\nThis checklist is concise for efficient QA of mission control outputs. Let me know if you want it expanded or formatted differently.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0398c7606ffc94200069af35637f788196bd1623ec01451c27\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-4.1-mini","usage":{"input":8512,"output":210,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8722,"cost":{"input":0.0034048000000000004,"output":0.00033600000000000004,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0037408000000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773090147199}}
